Share this on WhatsAppA girl has been killed by stray bullets fired by men of the Lagos police command to disperse the Yoruba nation agitators rallying at Ojota.
The girl, identified as Jumoke, was said to be arranging yoghurt in a shop when the bullet hit her, killing her right there, the Punch reported
People ar already gathering at the spot, fuelling the anger of the protesting crowd.
